N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 96.2 - Computation of permit fees

State Regulations

The fee for any such permit shall be equal to the
respective annual fee specified in the Alcoholic Beverage Control Law
multiplied by the number of years for which such permit is
issued. Notes
